### Basic Habit Demo Tests
### This file tests the basic-habit workflow that demonstrates if, loop, and string utils

@baseUrl = http://localhost:13000

### Check API Health
# @name healthCheck
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
Accept: application/json

### List Available Workflows
# @name workflowsList
GET {{baseUrl}}/misc/workflows
Accept: application/json

### Execute Basic Habit Demo Workflow
# @name executeBasicHabit
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/basic-habit-demo
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Execute with Custom Input (if you want to test with custom data)
# @name executeWithInput
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/basic-habit-demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": {}
}

### Check Workflow Status
# @name workflowStatus
GET {{baseUrl}}/misc/workflows/basic-habit-demo
Accept: application/json
